---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/ui/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="Organization | Agora" description="Understanding the distributed structure and the sponsor system of our community.">
  
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 bg-olive-50 text-olive-900">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-24">
      
      <Header>
        <span slot="surtitle">
          System Architecture
        </span>
        <fragment slot="header">
          The Structure
        </fragment>
        <fragment slot="subtitle">
          Agora’s structure combines the resilience of interpersonal bonds with the power of mass organization. We are a mesh, not a monolith.
        </fragment>
      </Header>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-olive-900 text-amber-400 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Level 01: The Bond</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-olive-950">The Sponsor System</h2>
          <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed">
            No one enters Agora alone. Every new member is paired with a <strong class="text-amber-700">Sponsor</strong>—a seasoned member who acts as a guide, a mentor, and an accountability partner.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-12 bg-white rounded-[3rem] border border-olive-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-4">
           <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-olive-100 border border-olive-200 flex items-center justify-center text-olive-400">
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
           </div>
           <div class="w-px h-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-olive-200 to-amber-500"></div>
           <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-olive-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow-lg shadow-olive-900/20">You</div>
           <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-amber-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Direct Accountability</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg mx-auto h-80 flex items-center justify-center bg-white rounded-[3rem] border border-olive-200 shadow-sm order-2 md:order-1 overflow-hidden">
          <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-olive-100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M50,40 L90,120 L10,120 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" class="opacity-50" />
            <line x1="50%" y1="10%" x2="90%" y2="40%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="90%" y1="40%" x2="75%" y2="90%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="75%" y1="90%" x2="25%" y2="90%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="25%" y1="90%" x2="10%" y2="40%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="10%" y1="40%" x2="50%" y2="10%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
          </svg>
          <div class="relative z-10 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-olive-900 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold uppercase shadow-xl border-4 border-white">
            <span class="text-amber-400 mb-1">Local</span>
            <span>Cell</span>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute top-[10%] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-amber-500 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-[40%] right-[10%] w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-olive-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[25%] w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-olive-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] left-[25%] w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-olive-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-[40%] left-[10%] w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-olive-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6 order-1 md:order-2">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-olive-900 text-amber-400 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Level 02: The Cell</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-olive-950">Distributed Chapters</h2>
          <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed">
            Chapters are local, autonomous nodes capped at <strong>Dunbar's Number</strong>. This ensures that every member of a cell actually knows, trusts, and supports every other member.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-olive-900 text-amber-400 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Level 03: The Movement</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-olive-950">Global Coordination</h2>
          <p class="text-olive-800 leading-relaxed">
            While action is local, strategy is global. Regional nodes connect to the <a href="/quorum" class="text-amber-700 underline decoration-amber-200 hover:decoration-amber-500 transition-all font-bold">Quorum</a> to synchronize efforts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg mx-auto h-80 flex items-center justify-center bg-white rounded-[3rem] border border-olive-200 shadow-sm p-8 overflow-hidden">
          <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-amber-100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="50%" y2="15%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="85%" y2="35%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="80%" y2="75%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="20%" y2="75%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
            <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="15%" y2="35%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
          </svg>
          <div class="relative z-10 w-28 h-28 rounded-full bg-olive-950 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-2 shadow-2xl border-4 border-amber-500/20">
            <span class="text-[8px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-500 mb-1">Strategic Core</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">The Quorum</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="map-section" class="space-y-12 pt-16 border-t border-olive-200">
        <div class="text-center space-y-2">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-olive-950 tracking-tight">Active Nodes</h2>
          <p class="text-amber-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-mono font-bold">The network is live</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-video bg-white rounded-[3rem] border border-olive-200 overflow-hidden shadow-inner group">
          <img 
            src="/world.svg" 
            alt="Movement Map" 
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-contain opacity-20 brightness-75 grayscale contrast-125 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-30"
          />

          <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-amber-500/20" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <line x1="25" y1="40" x2="48" y2="30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2" />
          </svg>

          <div class="absolute top-[40%] left-[25%]">
            <span class="absolute inline-flex h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-amber-400 animate-ping opacity-40"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-amber-600 border-2 border-white shadow-sm"></span>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute top-[30%] left-[48%]">
            <span class="absolute inline-flex h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-amber-400 animate-ping opacity-40"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-amber-600 border-2 border-white shadow-sm"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-center text-xs text-olive-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest max-w-lg mx-auto bg-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full border border-olive-100 shadow-sm">
          Security protocol: Locations restricted to verified members.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>